README
======

What is Solidocs?
----------------

Solidocs is a PHP MVC framework. Solidocs is a very light and works right out
of the box. The word "Solidocs" is a combination of Solid + Docs (documents).

Solidocs comes bundled with the Solidcms package and the Soliadmin package.
Solidcms is a complete Content Management System (CMS) and Solidadmin is the
built-in admin interface.

Requirements
------------

Solidocs is supposed to work with PHP 5.2 and up but PHP 5.3 is recommended.

Documentation
-------------

There is not yet any documentation available for Solidocs.